'''夏默学院史'''（'''{{lang-en|history of Shimer College}}'''）是關於[[夏默学院|夏默学院]]的歷史與沿革，最早可追溯自1853年，該學院曾牽涉一連串的危機與深層變革。由於這些原因，學院經常以[[鳳凰_(西方)|浴火鳳凰]]來象徵祂從灰燼中重生。<ref name="koukal">{{cite web|title=Coming Home Again|author=David R. Koukal|date=2009-10-17|url=http://alumni.shimer.edu/s/1028/images/editor_documents/News%20Items/Coming%20Home%20Again.pdf|accessdate=2010-04-20|archive-date=2010-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609192247/http://alumni.shimer.edu/s/1028/images/editor_documents/News%20Items/Coming%20Home%20Again.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="phoenix">Eric Nicholson (1973). "[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ySnJHPzFvB0 Phoenix Fly] {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ySnJHPzFvB0 |date=20160329191655 }}".</ref>

